{"type":"text","timestamp":1782445975032,"sessionID":"ses_0fdf4a05effeh4r8v5bdsW2oKc","part":{"id":"prt_f020f02ee0018txvxa8SGHUAS4","messageID":"msg_f020eee08001V4Dw3E6Y77iESh","sessionID":"ses_0fdf4a05effeh4r8v5bdsW2oKc","type":"text","text":"Updated phase-06 batch evidence for the `com/example` verification scope without changing target app code.\n\nChanged files:\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`: closed the 3 phase-06 source-test rows as replaced-by-target-verification with precise target endpoints, mapped source/target behavior, and fresh phase-06 harness-blocked evidence.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`: synced from the authority patch.\n- `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/test-build-report.md`: new phase-06 test-gate report from the bounded reproduction.\n- `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/test-build-report.json`: structured phase-06 test-gate result.\n- `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/test-build.log`: raw test-gate log.\n\nCommands run:\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\reports\\test_build_report.py --workspace-root D:\\workspace\\Foodike --target-project D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony --output-dir D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs --phase phase-06-polish-tests-verification --target aarch64-linux-ohos --timeout 600`\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix --authority D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json --patch C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\opencode\\phase06_matrix_patch.json --markdown D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.md --plan-json D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json --target-project D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n\nBuild result:\n- FAIL: test gate blocked, not app build blocked.\n- Current report: `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/test-build-report.md`\n- First blocker: `ld.lld: error: cannot open Scrt1.o: No such file or directory`\n\nWhat I changed:\n- Marked `app-src-androidtest-java-com-example-foodike-exampleinst-7ce120cd33-001-source-side-tests-or-verification-assets` as `implemented`.\n- Marked `app-src-test-java-com-example-foodike-exampleunittest-kt-7340d393c5-001-source-side-tests-or-verification-assets` as `implemented`.\n- Marked `app-src-test-java-com-example-foodike-exampleunittest-kt-504d70964f-002-crud-mutation-or-persistent-state-update` as `implemented`.\n- For all three rows, added:\n  - concrete `sourceBehavior`\n  - concrete `targetBehavior`\n  - `parityLevel: equivalent`\n  - precise `targetEndpoints`\n  - mapped `tests`\n  - fresh `verificationEvidence`\n  - aligned `coverageFacts` with `closureKind: implemented`, `parityKind: equivalent`, `factsSource: agent`\n  - `verification.testEvidence.kind: harness-blocked` pointing to the phase-06 report\n\nWhy no code changes were needed:\n- The target already contains focused replacement tests:\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj`\n  - `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj`\n- Those tests already map to real translated behavior in:\n  - `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/data/session/login_preferences_service.cj`\n  - `.../features/startup/startup_store.cj`\n  - `.../features/login/login_store.cj`\n  - `.../features/home/home_store.cj`\n  - `.../features/history/history_store.cj`\n  - `.../features/detail/detail_store.cj`\n  - `.../features/cart/cart_store.cj`\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- Target test harness remains blocked for this phase by linker/runtime kit resolution:\n  - `Scrt1.o`\n  - `crti.o`\n  - `crtn.o`\n  - `-lm`\n  - `-lc`\n- I did not keep editing test package config because the session rules capped harness work to one focused reproduction plus one focused config lookup, and that was enough to confirm the blocker remains current in phase 06.\n\nContradictions checked:\n- `plan.md` says phase 06 should add focused tests and verification evidence. The focused tests already exist; this batch now records them as the replacement evidence for the two source boilerplate tests and the placeholder CRUD row.\n- No current-phase platform capability rows were assigned, so no platform authority update was needed.\n- I did not close the unmatched `phase-06-resource-and-evidence-closeout` plan group because this batch was explicitly narrowed to the verification groups only.\n\nNext recommended action:\n- Start a dedicated test-harness repair session for `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-06-polish-tests-verification/test-build-report.md`, focused only on the missing HarmonyOS linker startup objects/libs so these existing target tests can become PASS evidence.","time":{"start":1782445966062,"end":1782445975028}}}
